data.whatILove:
You’ll want to spend lots of time in the fabulous great room of this 3-bedroom, 2-bath ranch. Highlighted with luxury vinyl plank floors, the room has vaulted ceilings, a gas corner fireplace, sliding barn door to hallway, ceiling fan and dining area, and opens into the kitchen. Everyone will enjoy entertaining and meal prep with slab granite countertops, mosaic tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, eat-in island with undermount sink, and shaker cabinets. 

The master suite has a vaulted ceiling with a ceiling fan, spacious walk-in closet and an ensuite bath with walk-in shower, dual sink vanity and plenty of storage.  There are two additional spacious bedrooms and the second bathroom with a shower/tub combination and vanity with tile counter. Up a flight of stairs is a 20’ x 10’ bonus room that can serve as a family room, playroom or fitness area. The home has central air and laundry closet off of the hallway. 

Out back is a covered patio with recessed lighting, immaculate landscaping, fenced lawn and there is a two-car attached garage for each door.
